    <p>ELLY was created to make tenant billing as simple as possible for building managers and tenants alike. Managing your tenants, billing, payments, meters, and invoices is as easy as logging into your account.</p>

    <p>Our aim is that with ELLY, worrying about tenant billing a thing of the past!</p>
    
