      <li>No more compiling utility data, creating invoices, and billing your tenants. Your tenants will pay their invoices online through ELLY.</li>
      <li>Your tenants will be automatically notified by email each month when their invoices are ready for viewing and payment</li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <li>Your ELLY account will be the central location for you to:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage your tenants</li>
        <li>Assign meters to your tenants</li>
        <li>View your tenants' month to month HVAC usage</li>
        <li>View your tenants' past invoices</li>
        <li>Change your billing preferences, e.g. days until due, billing cycle start date, etc.</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>

  </div>
</div>

